00:19.567 --> 00:20.867
Wow. Wow what?

00:20.902 --> 00:22.936
Griffin was right. I think I might like you.

00:22.970 --> 00:25.472
Ben, come in.

00:25.506 --> 00:26.807
I want to get married.

00:26.841 --> 00:28.041
Me, too.

00:28.076 --> 00:29.109
I never slept with her.

00:29.143 --> 00:31.278
You slept with her in Chicago. I did not.

00:34.916 --> 00:37.584
Some guy outside said to give this to you.

00:37.618 --> 00:39.486
